    "description": "游戏评测<br><br>&quot;黏土动画般的德国怪奇物语&quot;  7.3/10  --  游民星空（Gamersky）<br><br>&quot;纯手工制景风格《墨池镇（Trüberbrook）》：独具匠心的画面，充满巧思的解谜&quot; --  机核（Gcores）<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/e5061f86487e1ba49026952e3b1dad3e.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/963070a60c10710e1e9bdf0beb1167e3.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=226 /></span><br><br><strong>《墨池镇（Trüberbrook）》是一款科幻题材的探索解密游戏。游戏内场景皆为纯手工打造，在这个奇幻的20世纪60年代的平行宇宙展开自己的冒险吧！</strong><br><br>你将扮演一位年轻的美国科学家汉斯·唐豪瑟，上世纪与60年代末前往欧洲旅游。你的目的地是墨池镇（Trüberbrook）这个前不着村后不着店的偏远德国山村。至于你为什么会来这种地方 - 那是因为这是你抽奖中的，不来白不来！一场本该放松的旅游，却意外的拯救了世界...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/dbdf7b3e1d4abaa04f8a34baaa944a79.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=188 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/cc8f34d866651fd2c600956de4215ea4.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>谜团！惊悚！神秘！一款科幻探索解密游戏！<br></li><li>扮演美国科学家唐豪瑟踏上这片陌生的土地<br></li><li>设定于20世纪60年代晚期的冷战德国农村<br></li><li>灵感来源于双峰，X档案，怪奇物语以及星际迷航<br></li><li>内含普世价值，例如爱情，友情，忠诚，自我发现和恐龙<br></li><li>纯手工打造迷你场景！<br></li><li>英语&amp;德语完整配音！<br></li><li>美妙的游戏原声<br></li><li>10小时紧张刺激的游戏体验！</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/ddb904e1ef3a62d4823e6cc595c8a710.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/91cd3086903d358f86f26fc5dab4845c.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=142 /></span><br><br>《墨池镇（Trüberbrook）》在2017年12月一经登上KICKSTARTER， 30个小时内就完成了众筹目标。感谢5078名众筹者的支持，游戏各个方面都获得了提升！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/c3966c0c11d4d9dc185c14cfd65afa23.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br><br>时值1967年。世界政局正围绕着冷战和越战波澜起伏，俄罗斯美国竞相登月。而与此同时在欧洲，从巴黎到柏林，学生们都走上了街头。<br>时局动荡不安，但在一个时光仿若凝固的德国偏远小镇里发生的事却无人了解。一位二十多岁的美国学生汉斯·唐豪瑟意外中奖获得了一次欧洲之旅。他既不认识目的地墨池镇（Trüberbrook），也不记得参与过抽奖...但他乐意暂时放下他量子物理学博士的工作，来到德国的这个墨池镇（Trüberbrook）放松一下。<br>但他抵达之后却发生了意外状况：一个神秘人闯入了他的旅馆房间抢走了他随身携带的物理学相关笔记。但谁会这么做呢？又是为了什么？他逐渐的认识了村里的村民和游客。这里的人之中看上去正常的只有一位来这里研究的年轻女性人类学家格雷琴。在唐豪瑟还没反应过来之前，他们就一起踏上了一场毕生难忘的冒险。而他很快发现，自己来到墨池镇（Trüberbrook）并非巧合，他必须担负起拯救世界的重任！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/028a65f400fd3e784183a9a83dafa612.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=230 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/e86cd325b450aeba15a6d16e25cfeb58.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br><br>随着故事发展，唐豪瑟遇见了古人类学家格雷琴，还有一位神秘的发明家泰福特。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/7abd53cb30a13e64d11d78bb8a01d046.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=208 /></span><br><br>汉斯·唐豪瑟是一个二十多岁的年轻物理学家。他聪明机智，好奇心强，待人友善。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/eaaf15ba54747f13997784394b24b3ae.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=208 /></span><br><br>格雷琴性格火爆；这位有些过分热情的古人类学家来到墨池镇（Trüberbrook）是为了解开围绕在这个村子的神秘疑云。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/f02d303f42082f1c8a2ef16d7f902c12.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=208 /></span><br><br>隐居的发明家拉扎勒斯·泰福特在抵达墨池镇（Trüberbrook）后很快的因为其出众牌技闻名。他买下这里的一座昂贵宅邸必有原因...他究竟有什么企图？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/b826d26da80bffad946619bfa2827592.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=184 /></span><br><br>墨池镇（Trüberbrook）有着许多性格迥异的村民，游客和路过之人，比如粗鄙但好心的旅馆老板特露德和她的女儿雷尼。还有一位经历过两次世界大战的男爵，一位当代阴谋论家等等。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/64ffa759b3830a5937f6f95bc43db98b.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br><br>本游戏最为出众的便是独特的视觉风格。游戏场景皆有制作团队纯手工打造！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/3055bf796c5a18c5bb62f2ef6b2b1a7c.poster.avif?t=1717681834\" width=680 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/3055bf796c5a18c5bb62f2ef6b2b1a7c.webm?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/3055bf796c5a18c5bb62f2ef6b2b1a7c.mp4?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>也许效率不高，但我们喜欢它！一片一片，一点一点的拼成了游戏的场景。每一个细节都是一点点手工制作出来的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/ef98d5fd8adb64b3c66bf73ad7e1f17c.poster.avif?t=1717681834\" width=680 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/ef98d5fd8adb64b3c66bf73ad7e1f17c.webm?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/ef98d5fd8adb64b3c66bf73ad7e1f17c.mp4?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏模型使用被称为摄影制图法的技术进行了数字化，并进行了后期再拓扑。这样我们就得到了与角色高度融合的，拥有高度细节的模型。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/77c5fe226ad9abd0cece8ba1e3f27ad5.poster.avif?t=1717681834\" width=680 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/77c5fe226ad9abd0cece8ba1e3f27ad5.webm?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/77c5fe226ad9abd0cece8ba1e3f27ad5.mp4?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>工作量很大，但也令人振奋！你也许会问，这么多细节是怎么做出来的？难道我们去抢来了圣诞老人南极工厂里的小精灵？答案是我们精巧专业的手工，加班加点，全年无休！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/d5ba23e7d283ff37f836da77b40373b6.poster.avif?t=1717681834\" width=680 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/d5ba23e7d283ff37f836da77b40373b6.webm?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/d5ba23e7d283ff37f836da77b40373b6.mp4?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每一个场景都进行了独立处理，并使用了真实光源。这让我们能够模拟不同时间，不同天气下的场景状况。就连季节变化都能用无数小小雪片手工堆出来。真的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/e66f83ced5e713d2510edc40b7ab0b6d.poster.avif?t=1717681834\" width=680 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/e66f83ced5e713d2510edc40b7ab0b6d.webm?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/e66f83ced5e713d2510edc40b7ab0b6d.mp4?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>墨池镇（Trüberbrook）中那令人着迷的美术风格因此达成。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/74da30be74b454b58f456328290c5029.poster.avif?t=1717681834\" width=680 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/74da30be74b454b58f456328290c5029.webm?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/74da30be74b454b58f456328290c5029.mp4?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/060c246aa9d6fc17e641c151c6aebc23.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br><br>《墨池镇（Trüberbrook）》是一款故事驱动的点击冒险游戏，注重于角色和剧情发展，也包含了解密元素来推进故事。解密内容与剧情息息相关。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/5feffed5492a2500299898c172feba5e.poster.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/5feffed5492a2500299898c172feba5e.webm?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/5feffed5492a2500299898c172feba5e.mp4?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>玩家将扮演唐豪瑟以第三人称穿行于诸多场景，远拉的镜头有着类似西洋景似的美妙感觉。故事将随着您与环境的互动，与其他人物的交流而逐渐推进。解密不仅有基于物品栏的物品解密，更要尝试说服其他角色，或者回答某些诡异的心理测试。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/2a43f946a14c9dc65fab7f5af396d2f5.poster.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/2a43f946a14c9dc65fab7f5af396d2f5.webm?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/2a43f946a14c9dc65fab7f5af396d2f5.mp4?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>我们对主机版游戏进行了创新性的手柄操作调整，让玩家能够独立于视角变动进行移动。PC玩家则可以自由选择传统的点击移动和主机版的手柄操作。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/4887d489178effa4091443f2f36c4d0d.poster.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/4887d489178effa4091443f2f36c4d0d.webm?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/4887d489178effa4091443f2f36c4d0d.mp4?t=1717681834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757300/extras/fb97ca1c5ad6c877a1df8664fa4bd946.avif?t=1717681834\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br><br>《墨池镇（Trüberbrook）》的原创音乐完美契合了游戏的氛围 - 类似某种宁静的厄运爵士。灵感来源于Tom Waits, Angelo Badalamenti, Mark Lanegan, Timber Timbre和Bohren &amp; der Club of Gore的部分作品。曲作者为Sebastian Nagel &amp; Albrecht Schrader。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >本地化</h2>我们花了不少时间让游戏的配音与故事相符。主角作为一堆德国人中的唯一美国人，唐豪瑟在美版配音中将操着一口纯正的美国英语，而其他的当地村民都将说正宗德味英语。",
